    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-lab-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4. Validation results demonstrate RH < 1 at all five operating points and pressure-head predictions within 3.1% of experimental data. The assessment team accepted the submission on the basis of these results. Note: validation evidence was generated under model configuration ansys-cfx-15-build-2024-08 (modelVersion 2024-q3-build-2); the current production solver baseline is 2026-q1-build-7. The team noted the configuration discrepancy but concluded the physics and numerical settings are equivalent between builds.",
